Are you sure that PAL Battletoads came first?  Gamefaqs and Wikipedia claim that it was released in early 1993 in Europe, but the copyright date in-game says 1991.  If anything, I think the PAL version of Battletoads is a port of the NTSC version to reduce or eliminate the blank lines.<br />PAL Battletoads also still uses the same exact unrolled display update code.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Fri Feb 19, 2010 11:22 pm</p><hr />
