<title type="html"><![CDATA[NES Smurfs NTSC conversion?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6065&amp;p=56824#p56824"><![CDATA[
A proper patch for this, Asterix, or any of several other PAL exclusives would probably have to rewrite the entire screen update system to unroll the VRAM transfer loops. Rare had to do this when porting Battletoads (E) to run on an NTSC system, and turning the screen on late was part of the solution.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Fri Feb 19, 2010 5:06 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
